      <h1>Delegering av myndighet etter naturmangfoldloven fra Klima- og milj&#xF8;departementet til Milj&#xF8;direktoratet</h1>
      <ul class="defaultList">
        <li data-li-identifier="1." data-name="1.">
          <article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1">
            <article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1">Myndighet etter lov 19. juni 2009 nr. 100 om forvaltning av naturens mangfold (naturmangfoldloven) delegeres til Milj&#xF8;direktoratet for f&#xF8;lgende bestemmelser: <ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-1"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-1-ledd-1">&#xA7; 17a f&#xF8;rste ledd</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-2"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-1">&#xA7; 17a tredje ledd</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-3"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-3-ledd-1">&#xA7; 18 f&#xF8;rste ledd for enkeltvedtak om uttak av lakse- og innlandsfisk, forskrift eller enkeltvedtak om uttak av vilt, og enkeltvedtak om uttak av rovvilt</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-4"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-4-ledd-1">&#xA7; 18 tredje ledd f&#xF8;rste punktum for uttak av lakse- og innlandsfisk og vilt</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-5"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-5-ledd-1">&#xA7; 18 tredje ledd tredje punktum for vilt (omfatter ikke rovvilt)</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-6"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-6-ledd-1">&#xA7; 20 annet ledd</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-7"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-7-ledd-1">&#xA7; 21 annet ledd</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-8"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-8-ledd-1">&#xA7; 22</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-9"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-9-ledd-1">&#xA7; 34 sjette ledd</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-10"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-10-ledd-1">&#xA7; 44 f&#xF8;rste ledd tredje punktum</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-11"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-11-ledd-1">&#xA7; 44 annet ledd</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-12"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-12-ledd-1">&#xA7; 44 femte ledd annet punktum</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-13"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-13-ledd-1">&#xA7; 45 f&#xF8;rste ledd</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-14"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-14-ledd-1">&#xA7; 45 tredje ledd fjerde punktum</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-15"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-15-ledd-1">&#xA7; 51 f&#xF8;rste ledd annet punktum</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-16"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-16-ledd-1">&#xA7; 62 f&#xF8;rste ledd hva gjelder tildeling eller delegering av forvaltningsmyndighet for et omr&#xE5;de vernet med hjemmel i naturmangfoldloven kap. V</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-17"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-17-ledd-1">&#xA7; 62 andre ledd f&#xF8;rste punktum</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-18"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-18-ledd-1">&#xA7; 62 andre ledd andre punktum</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-19"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-19-ledd-1">&#xA7; 62 annet ledd tredje punktum</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-20"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-20-ledd-1">&#xA7; 63</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-21"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-21-ledd-1">&#xA7; 64</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-22"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-22-ledd-1">&#xA7; 65</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-23"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-23-ledd-1">&#xA7; 67</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-24"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-24-ledd-1">&#xA7; 68 hva gjelder myndigheten til &#xE5; foreta endringer av hvilken informasjon om enkeltvedtak som skal registreres i Milj&#xF8;vedtaksregisteret og hvordan enkeltvedtak skal stedfestes, jf. forskrift om Milj&#xF8;vedtaksregisteret &#xA7; 4 annet og tredje ledd</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-25"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-25-ledd-1">&#xA7; 69</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-26"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-26-ledd-1">&#xA7; 70 annet ledd</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-27"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-27-ledd-1">&#xA7; 71 f&#xF8;rste ledd</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-28"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-28-ledd-1">&#xA7; 72 tredje ledd</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-29"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-29-ledd-1">&#xA7; 73 f&#xF8;rste ledd</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-30"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-30-ledd-1">&#xA7; 73 fjerde ledd</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-31"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-31-ledd-1">&#xA7; 74 f&#xF8;rste og annet ledd</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-32"><article class="legalP" id="punkt-1-ledd-1-punkt-32-ledd-1">&#xA7; 77 hva gjelder myndighet til &#xE5; oppheve fredning av tr&#xE6;r og myndighet etter delegeringsvedtak 3. november 1988 nr. 4324. Endringen trer i kraft straks.</article></article></li></ul></article>
          </article>
        </li>
        <li data-li-identifier="2." data-name="2.">
          <article class="listArticle" id="punkt-2">
            <article class="legalP" id="punkt-2-ledd-1">Delegeringene trer i kraft 15. mars 2025. Delegeringene er ikke til hinder for at departementet kan ut&#xF8;ve myndighet etter bestemmelsene.</article>
          </article>
        </li>
        <li data-li-identifier="3." data-name="3.">
          <article class="listArticle" id="punkt-3">
